energy.usef.core.config

Enum ConfigParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ConfigParam>
      • energy.usef.core.config.ConfigParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ConfigParam>

    public enum ConfigParam
extends Enum<ConfigParam>
    The Config parameter contains all configuration parameters which can be used in the core libraries of USEF. Parameters which are participant specific are defined in the classes ConfigParam. The property class is used to do some validations on the parameter. Also a user defined class can be entered with user specific validations, e.g. a parameter should be integer and positive. An enumeration is used to configure the parameters to define the config parameter more type safe (before a string value was used).
